com.icfolson.aem.monitoring.core.filter

Interface MonitoringFilter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    NewRelicFilter

    public interface MonitoringFilter
    The service interface for a monitoring filters. If no context property is set, the filter will be executed when a monitoring entity is submitted (an "input" filter). To filter after input, but before outputting the entity to a specific writer implementation, set the context to the name of the desired writer. In both cases, the 'service.ranking' property is respected.
